This endpoint retrieves all `Events` for the given `Account`.

### HTTP Request

`GET https://api.tito.io/:account/events`

### Query Parameters

Parameter | Default | Description
--------- | ------- | -----------
include | | A comma separated list specify of related resources to include. Options: `releases`

